1. *Vrag* mi je odneo novčanik. (The devil took my wallet.)
2. Zašto radiš to? Zar *vrag* neće da te kazni? (Why are you doing that? Won't the devil punish you?)
3. Nemoj da se igraš sa *vragom*, moglo bi biti opasno. (Don't play with the devil, it could be dangerous.)
4. Ko je *vrag* uzeo moj telefon? (Who the hell took my phone?)
5. *Vrag* mi nije dao da se naspavam. (The devil didn't let me sleep.)
6. Pobogu, koji *vrag* ti je? (For God's sake, what the hell is wrong with you?)
7. Sve ide po zlu, *vraga* nema! (Everything is going wrong, there's no sign of the devil!)
8. Drži se dalje od njega, to je pravi *vrag*. (Stay away from him, he's a real devil.)
9. Kao da me je *vrag* naterao da uradim to. (It's as if the devil made me do it.)
10. Koliko puta moram da ti kažem da ne praviš posao sa *vragom*? (How many times do I have to tell you not to make a deal with the devil?)